{"tid":2268887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴建議認罪否則停法律支援　響號被捕車長拒絕　","createTime":"2020-11-03T06:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T06:33:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ea77e0e6b4f0774d50184b09a47226f97e1872","tid":2268887,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"網民今年 9 月 6 日發起九龍區遊行，期間警方在彌敦道截停一部 970 號新巴，拘捕一名 36 歲巴士司機涉「危險駕駛」，最後落案控告「不小心駕駛」，案件本月 17 日再訊。新巴職工會會長林錦標向《立場新聞》表示，一直表示會向涉事司機提供法律支援的新巴，經律師團隊評估後，昨日（2 日）建議司機認罪；又表示如不認罪，就不會再提供法律支援。林錦標表示涉事司機將繼續抗辯，工會已安排律師支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/新巴建議認罪否則停法律支援-響號車長-拒絕-獲工會另安排律師/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E5%81%9C%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-%E9%9F%BF%E8%99%9F%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7-%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E7%8D%B2%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%A6%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0En88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=59a8e58a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E5%81%9C%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-%E9%9F%BF%E8%99%9F%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7-%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E7%8D%B2%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%A6%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%2F&h=2b318115\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/新巴建議認罪否則停法律支援-響號車長-拒絕-獲工會另安排律師/</a>"}]}